life cycle function:
Component will be called automatically at some time.

1. Initialization: setup props and state (constructor)


2. Mounting:
  componentWillMount
  render
  componentDidMount:  called once, could put AJAX in it

3. Updating:

 - props:
    componentWillReceiveProps(when the comp EXISTS and prop changed) - shouldCompon....
 - states:
    shouldComponentUpdate(false / true) - componentWillUpdate - render - componentDidUpdate

4. Unmounting: componentWillUnmount
